  "reference_number": "RUS2147",
  "remarks": "\nRED BOX ENERGY SERVICES PTE LTD is an involved person under the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 based on the following ground: RED BOX ENERGY SERVICES PTE LTD has been involved in obtaining a benefit from or supporting the Government of Russia by making available goods or technology to a person carrying on business in a sector of strategic significance to the Government of Russia, namely the Russian energy sector.\n",
